source: crates/biome_formatter_test/src/snapshot_builder.rs
info: yaml/spec/spec-example-6-13-reserved-directives.yml
---

# Input

```yml
%FOO  bar baz # Should be ignored
              # with a warning.
--- "foo"

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,4 +1,3 @@
-%FOO bar baz # Should be ignored
-# with a warning.
----
-"foo"
+%FOO  bar baz # Should be ignored
+              # with a warning.
+--- "foo"
```

# Output

```yml
%FOO  bar baz # Should be ignored
              # with a warning.
--- "foo"
```
